    "Zheng et al. 2017), and model-based features (e.g. Rivas-Villar et al. 2021).",
    "Table 4 in Appendix A categorize and summarize various features used for plankton recognition.",
    "The most commonly used image feature type in plankton recognition is shape features (see e.g.",
    "Sosik and Olson 2007; Zetsche et al. 2014) that characterize either the contour or binary mask of the object (plankton).",
